  "title": "技术分享会",
  "description": "每周技术分享交流",
  "location": "教学楼A301",
  "startTime": "2025-11-18T14:00:00",
  "endTime": "2025-11-18T16:00:00",
  "maxParticipants": 1,
  "rewardPoints": 5
}

### 34. 用户2报名第二个活动
POST {{baseUrl}}/activity/2/join
Authorization: Bearer {{user2Token}}

